---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Card from '../components/ui/Card.astro';
import Badge from '../components/ui/Badge.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Disclaimer - FinCalcLab"
  description="Read our Disclaimer. FinCalcLab calculations are for educational and informational purposes only. Do not treat projections as formal financial advice."
>
  <div class="static-page-wrapper">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px;">
      <div class="text-center" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-8);">
        <Badge variant="neutral">Disclaimer</Badge>
        <h1 style="margin-top: var(--space-2); font-size: 2.5rem; letter-spacing: -0.04em;">Disclaimer</h1>
        <p style="font-size: 1.15rem; color: var(--color-text-muted);">Please read this disclaimer carefully before using our calculators and tools.</p>
      </div>

      <Card elevation="sm" style="padding: var(--space-8); border-color: var(--color-border);">
        <div class="article-content">
          <p>
            The website <strong>FinCalcLab.com</strong> provides financial calculators, projections, guides, and tools free of charge. By using this website, you acknowledge and agree to the terms of this Disclaimer.
          </p>

          <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: var(--space-6); margin-bottom: var(--space-3); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); padding-bottom: var(--space-1);">1. Not Financial or Professional Advice</h2>
          <p>
            All content and calculations available on this site are for **informational and educational purposes only**. FinCalcLab.com is not a registered financial advisor, broker, accountant, or tax planner. 
          </p>
          <p>
            The outputs and projections generated by our calculators are mathematical models based on formulas and user inputs; they do not guarantee future performance, returns, or exact tax liabilities. You should not treat any results as formal tax, legal, investment, or financial planning advice.
          </p>

          <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: var(--space-6); margin-bottom: var(--space-3); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); padding-bottom: var(--space-1);">2. "As-Is" and Accuracy of Models</h2>
          <p>
            We make every reasonable effort to keep our calculations accurate, up-to-date, and compliant with relevant guidelines (such as the Union Budget of India 2025 tax updates). However, calculations are provided on an **"as-is" and "as-available"** basis without warranty of any kind. 
          </p>
          <p>
            Real-world returns are subject to inflation, management fees, market volatility, currency fluctuations, and localized tax structures that may not be captured by these models.
          </p>

          <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: var(--space-6); margin-bottom: var(--space-3); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); padding-bottom: var(--space-1);">3. Professional Consultation Recommended</h2>
          <p>
            We highly recommend consulting a qualified, certified public accountant (CPA), registered investment advisor (RIA), or localized tax consultant before executing any financial plans, investing in mutual funds, or filing tax returns. Decisions made based on calculations on this website are entirely at your own risk.
          </p>

          <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: var(--space-6); margin-bottom: var(--space-3); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); padding-bottom: var(--space-1);">4. Third-Party Links & Ads</h2>
          <p>
            This website may contain links to outside websites or display advertisements (such as Google AdSense). FinCalcLab.com does not endorse, control, or take responsibility for the content, privacy policies, or practices of third-party websites or ad partners.
          </p>
        </div>
      </Card>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .static-page-wrapper {
    padding-top: var(--space-12);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-16);
  }

  .article-content p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }
</style>
